{"tid":2511057,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警收指令：離開理大即當暴動","createTime":"2021-04-30T15:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T15:24:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"09fe9ea131deed90209ccbeaf898842fa66fe720","tid":2511057,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:06:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210430/U7WY5LRMP5HULKUVT3CN7T3QDY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210430%2FU7WY5LRMP5HULKUVT3CN7T3QDY%2F&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRBx0icFY2nnrImD0qQ%2FuO9w%3D&h=549ed4f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210430%2FU7WY5LRMP5HULKUVT3CN7T3QDY%2F&h=7f8fc1f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210430/U7WY5LRMP5HULKUVT3CN7T3QDY/</a><br />\n<br />\n警收指令：離開理大即當暴動<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9JPqqkZS5S5dWh8s08Sp9bzSfMA=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JBLMQZY2X5GRLD72SJZIRW57XE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9JPqqkZS5S5dWh8s08Sp9bzSfMA%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJBLMQZY2X5GRLD72SJZIRW57XE.jpg&h=556bc6bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員胡景輝<br />\n<br />\n【藏士巴拿案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】前年11月理大圍城衝突期間，一名男學生在理大附近路軌被捕及搜出兩支⼠巴拿，被控管有非法用途工具罪受審。拘捕被告的警員供稱，案發時看見三名可疑男子從隧道跑出，並欲向他掟石，又丟下背包，故向他們發射了兩發橡膠子彈，三人隨即分頭逃走。其中被告欲沿路軌逃走，但遭截停，並在其背包搜出兩個只有手指及手掌般長的士巴拿。警員又透露，當日上級指令要以暴動罪名拘捕任何從理大出來的人。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱射橡膠彈時三人「企定定」<br />\n<br />\n控方唯一證人警員胡景輝指，前年11月17日因理工大學內發生暴動，小隊在附近設立防線禁止身處理大內的人離開。晚上10時收到指示，如有人從理大出來，全數以暴動罪名拘捕。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n胡自稱。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n盤問下，胡才稱三人其實沒掟出石頭，僅稱見到他們手持的是碎石。辯方質疑，胡在警員記事冊中只寫下他們用「雜物」掟警，胡解釋因寫記事冊的時間倉卒，故在口供補充。胡又指他射橡膠子彈時三人是「企定定」，因當時他們未分辨到哪條路可安全離開。胡在庭上檢視證物，胡同意士巴拿體積不大。辯方指出，士巴拿在袋內需「摷到落底」，不易取出。胡重複回應「唔記得、冇印象」。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官梁嘉琪裁定案件表證成立。案件押後至6月17日結案陳詞。案件編號：KCCC837/20"},{"pid":"f5cc3e145d0d5f6b7f9d5193900c55675b21b73e","tid":2511057,"uid":374209,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:08:57.000Z","msg":"原來大家怪錯cctoy 離開就當暴動 怪唔得知Cctoy叫全部人翻理大 原來真係堡壘<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ncctoy好有先見之明<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d54a22f58db2aa64a490d49fe45e873905ea26","tid":2511057,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:11:19.000Z","msg":"全部同我返poly<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca685b5e171d466ba435602d8602abc427b95aa","tid":2511057,"uid":31215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f5cc3e145d0d5f6b7f9d5193900c55675b21b73e","tid":2511057,"uid":374209,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:08:57.000Z","msg":"原來大家怪錯cctoy 離開就當暴動 怪唔得知Cctoy叫全部人翻理大 原來真係堡壘<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ncctoy好有先見之明<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:11:39.000Z","msg":"On9私怨撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩都要扯去抽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0e053a48011c420da0a0c01ba7fa94d5e0e555","tid":2511057,"uid":374209,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4ca685b5e171d466ba435602d8602abc427b95aa","tid":2511057,"uid":31215,"like":4,"dis